---
title: Synthesis — Phase 3 (Blindspot Detection + Verdict Synthesis)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant ORC as Orchestrator<br/>(Temporal Workflow)
    participant TEMPORAL as Temporal
    participant REDIS as Redis Streams
    participant BS as blindspot-detector<br/>(Temporal Worker)
    participant SYNTH as synthesizer<br/>(Temporal Worker)

    Note over ORC,SYNTH: Precondition: all 6 parallel agents STOP received.<br/>Phase 3a — Blindspot Detection

    ORC->>REDIS: XRANGE all 9 preceding agent streams<br/>collect observations for blindspot input

    ORC->>TEMPORAL: schedule activity: blindspot-detector<br/>({run_id, upstream_observations: [all 9 agent obs]})
    TEMPORAL->>BS: execute activity

    BS->>BS: analyze observations from<br/>all 9 preceding agents

    BS->>BS: compute coverage asymmetry score<br/>left=12 SUPPORTIVE, center=8 CRITICAL,<br/>right=11 CRITICAL -> no major blindspot

    BS->>REDIS: XADD ... type=START phase=synthesis
    BS->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(BLINDSPOT_SCORE, 0.12, F)<br/>publish(BLINDSPOT_DIRECTION, NONE, F)<br/>publish(CROSS_SPECTRUM_CORROBORATION, FALSE, F)
    BS->>REDIS: XADD progress:claim-4821-run-003 *<br/>agent=blindspot-detector event=observations_published
    BS->>REDIS: XADD ... type=STOP finalStatus=F

    BS-->>TEMPORAL: activity complete
    TEMPORAL-->>ORC: activity result

    ORC->>REDIS: XREADGROUP — consume STOP
    ORC->>ORC: blindspot-detector = COMPLETE

    Note over ORC,SYNTH: Phase 3b — Synthesis<br/>All 10 preceding agents complete.<br/>Orchestrator assembles consolidated observation log.

    ORC->>REDIS: XRANGE all 10 agent streams<br/>collect F/C status observations

    ORC->>TEMPORAL: schedule activity: synthesizer<br/>({run_id, consolidated_observations: [all F/C obs from 10 agents]})
    TEMPORAL->>SYNTH: execute activity

    Note over SYNTH: Synthesizer applies DetermineOBXResolution<br/>DMN to resolve authoritative value per code.<br/>Computes weighted confidence score.

    SYNTH->>SYNTH: resolve authoritative obs per code<br/>apply confidence weights:<br/>  claimreview_match: 0.35<br/>  domain_evidence: 0.30<br/>  cross_spectrum: 0.20<br/>  blindspot_penalty: -0.10<br/>  -> CONFIDENCE_SCORE = 0.31

    SYNTH->>SYNTH: map 0.31 -> MOSTLY_FALSE<br/>(range: 0.25-0.44)

    SYNTH->>REDIS: XADD ... type=START phase=synthesis
    SYNTH->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(CONFIDENCE_SCORE, 0.31, F)<br/>publish(VERDICT, MOSTLY_FALSE, F)<br/>publish(VERDICT_NARRATIVE, "...", F)<br/>publish(SYNTHESIS_SIGNAL_COUNT, 28, F)<br/>publish(SYNTHESIS_OVERRIDE_REASON, "", F)

    Note over SYNTH: Checks if VERDICT differs from CLAIMREVIEW_VERDICT.<br/>PolitiFact said MOSTLY_FALSE. System agrees.<br/>SYNTHESIS_OVERRIDE_REASON left empty.

    SYNTH->>REDIS: XADD progress:claim-4821-run-003 *<br/>agent=synthesizer event=verdict_emitted
    SYNTH->>REDIS: XADD ... type=STOP finalStatus=F

    SYNTH-->>TEMPORAL: activity complete
    TEMPORAL-->>ORC: activity result

    ORC->>REDIS: XREADGROUP — consume STOP
    ORC->>ORC: synthesizer = COMPLETE<br/>all 11 agents complete<br/>status = completed

    Note over ORC: completed state triggers session finalization.<br/>Orchestrator workflow proceeds to finalization steps.
